headline: SolarEdge Technologies Q4 Loss Wider Than Expected, Revenues Down Y/Y
summary: SEDG's Q4 revenues of $196.2 million surpass the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 5.3%. However, the top line declines 37.9% from the year-ago quarter's level.
